<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Acadia Activation Mail</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 600px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #007AFF;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #555;
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-top: 0;
        }

        p {
            color: #555;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .activation-code {
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 20px;
        }

        a {
            color: #007AFF;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome to Acadia!</h1>
        <h2>An E-Learning Platform</h2>
        <p>Hello <strong><%= user.firstName %></strong>,</p>
        <p>We're thrilled to have you on board! You are now a part of our learning community, where knowledge meets opportunity.</p>
        <p>To get started, use the activation code below:</p>
        <div class="activation-code"><%= activationCode %></div>
        <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to contact our support team at <a href="mailto:opuscorppune@gmail.com">opuscorppune@gmail.com</a>.</p>
        <p>Happy learning!</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
